data.description: Welcome Home to a spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in River Club subdivision with Swim/Tennis/Play! This home features a welcoming foyer, formal living room, formal dining room, eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar and pantry which leads into the a huge spacious family room with a fireplace. There's a half bath on the main level and 2 additional bathrooms on the upper level. Upstairs offers a primary private en-suite, soaking tub, double vanities & dual closets!!! The secondary bedrooms are oversized as well with the 4th bedroom large enough to be 2 rooms. Two car garage, driveway, backyard patio & exterior storage shed. This house is a must see! Seller is relocating, and motivated. Seller is also willing to contribute to closing cost. Bring your offers!
